00:36:32.964 --> 00:36:36.624
In the study, there was 28 tumor biopsies that

639
00:36:36.684 --> 00:36:40.316
wereprotein sequenced. And

640
00:36:40.576 --> 00:36:43.616
across the entire cohort, we found over 2,000 proteins.

