00:37:21.416 --> 00:37:22.936
had an AUC of 96%

652
00:37:23.776 --> 00:37:25.976
when we tried to classify tumor versus normal tissue.

653
00:37:26.856 --> 00:37:27.756
This is quite cool though,

654
00:37:28.716 --> 00:37:29.996
even though it was a really small study.

655
00:37:31.716 --> 00:37:34.916
And when we looked at the principal component analysis, again, this is all just on

656
00:37:34.956 --> 00:37:37.856
protein-level data, you can see that the proteome is really

