00:37:38.936 --> 00:37:42.855
well-equipped to tease apart the different tumor versus normal

658
00:37:43.076 --> 00:37:43.456
patients.

659
00:37:45.296 --> 00:37:47.626
We then looked at a study on pancreatic cancer,

