00:38:37.436 --> 00:38:38.516
So in this study,

674
00:38:39.376 --> 00:38:43.326
there was increase in ECM remodeling again, which is a common theme that

675
00:38:43.336 --> 00:38:46.556
we see. And there was increased inflammatory

676
00:38:46.976 --> 00:38:47.536
mediators.

677
00:38:48.636 --> 00:38:52.176
And again, some of the proteins that we saw in this, and this now is soluble

678
00:38:52.196 --> 00:38:53.616
proteome, which is plasma proteomics,

679
00:38:54.796 --> 00:38:58.296
were again shown to be for the first time in African patients.

680
00:38:59.616 --> 00:39:03.556
Something that we really liked was the LGR1

