00:40:44.076 --> 00:40:47.716
12 of these proteins were linked to nerve function, and this is something that the

708
00:40:47.736 --> 00:40:49.516
collaborator was really interested in.

709
00:40:49.876 --> 00:40:51.936
She wanted to know what was the

710
00:40:53.856 --> 00:40:57.476
involvement of the nervous system in how cancers metastasize.

