00:42:04.056 --> 00:42:05.936
driving chemoresistance and metastasis?

731
00:42:07.196 --> 00:42:11.116
And I guess further to that is because there's this kind of shield around

732
00:42:11.156 --> 00:42:12.856
the tumor,

733
00:42:14.196 --> 00:42:17.936
are we then unable to get drugs into the tumor to actually

