1327
01:18:32.608 --> 01:18:33.088
exciting

1328
01:18:33.988 --> 01:18:37.668
finding of the MECOM short isoform focal

1329
01:18:37.828 --> 01:18:41.188
gain being more associated with African ancestry,

1330
01:18:41.968 --> 01:18:45.808
having an association with worse clinical out-- and having an

1331
01:18:45.848 --> 01:18:48.418
association with worse clinical outcomes.

1332
01:18:49.538 --> 01:18:53.128
There's still more work to do, of course, that we need to functionally validate

